com.valentine.esp.statemachines

Class GetAlertData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.valentine.esp.statemachines.GetAlertData

  • public class GetAlertData
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the class that aggregates the Alert Data responses into an ArrayList representing all of the current alerts. Used internally by the Valentine Client.
